The paper deals with transmission schemes for a two-way relay channel using physical layer network coding with space-time coding. This involves techniques related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and communication (cs.NI), system and control theory (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
